OL,3,CPlans for Cumbrian Mayor progress to
OL,4,Cthe next stage
OL,6,FCumbria has moved a step closer to
OL,7,Fgetting a directly elected mayor with
OL,8,Fmore powers over areas including
OL,9,Ftransport and housing.
OL,11,FMembers of Westmorland and Furness
OL,12,FCouncil's Cabinet said today they were
OL,13,F'minded to consent' to the
OL,14,Festablishment of a new Mayoral-led
OL,15,Fauthority for the county.
OL,17,FA final decision on whether to approve
OL,18,Fthe proposals will be made by
OL,19,FCumbria's two unitary councils on 14
OL,20,FOctober.
