OL,3,CPlans for Cumbrian Mayor progress to
OL,4,Cthe next stage
OL,6,FThe decision is a step towards the
OL,7,Festablishment of a Mayoral Combined
OL,8,FAuthority (MCA) for the county which
OL,9,Fwould see new powers devolved from
OL,10,Fcentral government as well as access
OL,11,Fto a multi-million pound investment
OL,12,Ffund over the next 30 years.
