OL,3,CPlans for Cumbrian Mayor progress to
OL,4,Cthe next stage
OL,6,FCouncil Leader, Councillor Jonathan
OL,7,FBrook, said: "This is clearly a very
OL,8,Fimportant step and, having weighed up
OL,9,Fall the available evidence, we believe
OL,10,Fthat establishing a Mayoral Combined
OL,11,FAuthority would be in the best
OL,12,Finterests of our residents,
OL,13,Fcommunities and businesses ` and
OL,14,Fensure that Cumbria is not left behind
OL,15,Fwhen it comes to investment.
