OL,3,CPlans for Cumbrian Mayor progress to
OL,4,Cthe next stage
OL,6,F"Moving decision-making away from
OL,7,FWestminster and closer to the people
OL,8,Fwhose lives those decisions will
OL,9,Faffect is a very positive step and one
OL,10,Fwe welcome. We are also mindful that
OL,11,FCumbria must have a seat alongside
OL,12,Fother areas of the north on important
OL,13,Fnational forums if the ambitions we
OL,14,Fhave for a better, stronger, more
OL,15,Finclusive economic future for all are
OL,16,Fto be realised.
