OL,3,CPlans for Cumbrian Mayor progress to
OL,4,Cthe next stage
OL,6,F"The sooner we have a combined
OL,7,Fauthority, the sooner we will get the
OL,8,Fbenefits, not just of a MCA, and a
OL,9,Fseat at various regional and national
OL,10,Fbodies, but we will move more quickly
OL,11,Ftowards additional powers reserved for
OL,12,Fan established authority.
OL,14,F"We have been given the opportunity,
OL,15,Fof a year to prepare and to shape
OL,16,Fthings and make use of funds and MCA
OL,17,Fstaff, to undertake much of the
OL,18,Fpreparatory work. This will be lost,
OL,19,Fif we say no.
