OL,3,CPlans for Cumbrian Mayor progress to
OL,4,Cthe next stage
OL,6,FThe decision will be made by both
OL,7,FCumberland Council and Westmorland and
OL,8,FFurness Council and if plans are
OL,9,Fapproved the Cumbria Combined
OL,10,FAuthority would be in place from 2026
OL,11,Fwith leadership elections to then take
OL,12,Fplace in 2027.
OL,14,FIf plans were approved and a mayor is
OL,15,Felected in 2027 then the new authority
OL,16,Fwould take over control of the Cumbria
OL,17,FPolice, Fire and Crime Commissioner
OL,18,Fand that role would be abolished.
